    dc:description "Figure 11. Taxonomic variation in the structure of ‘blurred calls’, visualized in RavenPro 1.5 (Cornell University). The black line divides calls that modulate upward in frequency (left) and downward in frequency (right); both types were detected in C. [f.] berlepschi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8326324/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8326332>
    dc:description "Figure 15. Ventral and dorsal views of the adult male plumages in C. b. berlepschi, C. b. caniceps, C. o.tenebris ssp. nov., C. b. nebulus ssp.nov., and C. mentalis. Photograph by M.R.H." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8326332/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8326334>
    dc:description "Figure 16. Ventral and dorsal views of the adult female plumages in C. b. berlepschi, C. b. caniceps, C. o.tenebris ssp. nov., C. b. nebulus ssp.nov., and C. mentalis. Photograph by M.R.H." ;
